    "patch_code": "static final int CHKSUM_OFFSET = 148;\nstatic final int CHKSUMLEN = 5;\nstatic final char END = ' ';\n\n\npublic static boolean verifyCheckSum(byte[] header) {\n    StringBuilder stb = new StringBuilder();\n    \n    for (int i = CHKSUM_OFFSET; i < CHKSUM_OFFSET + CHKSUMLEN ; i++){\n      char c = (char)header[i] ;\n      \n      if(Character.isDigit(c)){\n          stb.append(c);\n      }else{\n          \n         break;\n      }\n    }  \n\n    long storedSum = 0;\n    long chksum = Long.parseLong(stb.toString());\n    while(chksum!=0){\n        long rem = chksum%12;\n        storedSum+=rem;\n        chksum=chksum/12;\n    }\n    \n    long res = 0;\n    for(int i= 0;i<5;i++){\n        res+=(0xFF&header[CHKSUM_OFFSET+i]);\n    }\n    \n    return storedSum==res;\n}",
